---
title: Prime Rib Cheeseburger with Grilled Onion Jam and Herby Garlic Hash
description: Treat yourself to a good ol' fashioned BBQ with our new prime rib burger! Top this bad boy with cheese curds and some of our sweet 'n' sticky no-fuss onion jam, and pair it with a delicious herby garlic hash. You will truly be #winning with this one!
